---
/**
 * Play-UI 03 · The Hinge Is Income — recreated from T03-IncomeHinge.astro
 */
import '../../../styles/global.css';
import '../../../styles/theme.css';
import '../../../styles/play-primitives.css';
---
<div class="play-canvas">
<section class="play-section play-glow" data-slot="03" data-variant="v1" style="justify-content: center;">
  <span class="play-kicker">03 / 11</span>

  <div style="max-width: 1400px;">
    <p class="play-eyebrow" style="margin: 0 0 24px;">The reframe</p>
    <h2 class="play-h1">
      The Apprenticeship Degree is a <span class="play-gradient">rural income engine</span> — the staffing fix is the side effect.
    </h2>
    <div class="play-rule" style="max-width: 224px; margin: 40px 0 32px;"></div>
    <p class="play-lede" style="max-width: 1024px;">
      Read for a rural-development funder, this isn't charity for under-resourced
      schools. It raises individual and household earnings, solves the employer's
      shortage with grow-your-own talent, and compounds as raised wages
      recirculate in the local economy.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
</div>
